{"type":"article","id":22233,"title":"北京大学教授：中共领导人子女宁可当外国人也不回来坐江山，我很捉急啊","uid":3685,"topics":[2968,1894,868,1186,3934],"contents":"北大社会学教授郑也夫教授近日撰文《为谁保江山》，指中国当下的统治集团子孙坐江山欲望弱化。<br>\n<br>\n“中国当下的统治集团遇到了一个人类历史上罕见的问题，就是特权阶层中高比例的子孙坐江山的欲望弱化，取而代之是移民海外的愿望。诸多原因促成了他们宁做美欧诸国之普通人，不作父母之邦的特权者。”<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Ed_34gfU4AYbSoq?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Ed_34gfU4AYbSoq?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Ed_34gfU4AYbSoq?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Ed_34gVU8AANH_x?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Ed_34gVU8AANH_x?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Ed_34gVU8AANH_x?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Ed_34ggU8AU_BDZ?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Ed_34ggU8AU_BDZ?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Ed_34ggU8AU_BDZ?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-07-28","agreeCount":8,"discussionCount":0}